reviewText:
I was expecting something else, but I did enjoy this short flick.  I wish they had some supporting material included about the philosophy and reasons for the mens shed program, but I have picked most of that up from other web sites.

This flick looks like it was a local production, and it was well done.  It gets over some of the reasons for a Mens Shed, but doesn't cover all the bases.  Still, I like it, but was just hoping for more.
